; Test value comparison between amount and integer
; Covers value.cc lines related to amount vs integer comparison

2024/01/15 Test
    Expenses:Food    $50.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/20 Test
    Expenses:Food    $30.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format="%(display_total > 60 ? \"big\" : \"small\")\n" Expenses
small
big
end test
